languages.text: "Ханейманн? Ты — не он, лжец. Деменц Ханейманн послушен мне, его разум открыт к голосам пустоты, а рожденный им мусорный код оберегает мой мир. И ты, ржавый отброс из касты отщепенцев-Эксплораторов, не смеешь нарекать меня "невежественным"!"

"Haneumann? Liar, you are not him. Dementz Haneumann obeys me, his mind is open to the voices of the void, and the scrap-code he created protects my world. And I'll not have you, rusted refuse from the misfit caste of Explorators, call me 'ignorant'!"

languages.text: “哈努曼？骗子，你才不是他呢。德曼兹·哈努曼服从于我，他的思想始终对虚空开放，他创造的废码保护着我的世界。我绝不允许让你这个来自开拓者种姓的生锈垃圾闯进来，说我是什么‘无知’的家伙！”

languages.text: «¿Haneumann? Miente, no es él. Dementz Haneumann me obedece, su mente está abierta a las voces del vacío y el código de chatarra que creó protege mi mundo. ¡Y no permitiré que un trozo de basura oxidada de la obsoleta casta exploradora me llame "ignorante"!».
languages.original_text: "Haneumann? Liar, you are not him. Dementz Haneumann obeys me, his mind is open to the voices of the void, and the scrap-code he created protects my world. And I'll not have you, rusted refuse from the misfit caste of Explorators, call me 'ignorant'!"

languages.text: 「ヘニュマン？嘘だ、お前が彼であるはずがない。デメンツ・へニュマンは私に従っていて、心は虚空の声を聞くために開き、奴が作成した破壊コードが私の惑星を守っている。それに、探検家などという錆びたゴミの適合者カーストごときが私を『無知』と呼ぶな！」
languages.original_text: "Haneumann? Liar, you are not him. Dementz Haneumann obeys me, his mind is open to the voices of the void, and the scrap-code he created protects my world. And I'll not have you, rusted refuse from the misfit caste of Explorators, call me 'ignorant'!"

languages.text: "Haneumann? Lügner, der seid Ihr nicht. Dementz Haneumann gehorcht mir, sein Geist steht den Stimmen der Leere offen, und sein Schadcode schützt meine Welt. Und ich lasse mich von Euch rostigem Müll aus der verkommenen Kaste der Exploratoren nicht 'ignorant' nennen!"
languages.original_text: "Haneumann? Liar, you are not him. Dementz Haneumann obeys me, his mind is open to the voices of the void, and the scrap-code he created protects my world. And I'll not have you, rusted refuse from the misfit caste of Explorators, call me 'ignorant'!"

languages.text: « Haneumann ? Mensonge ! Ce n'est pas vous ! Dementz Haneumann m'obéit. Son esprit est réceptif aux voix du Vide et l'anticode qu'il a créé protège mon monde. Je ne laisserai pas un rebut rouillé de la caste marginale des Explorators me traiter d'ignorant ! »

languages.text: "Haneumann mı? Yalancı, o sen değilsin. Dementz Haneumann bana itaat eder. Zihni uçsuzun seslerine açıktır ve yarattığı hurda kodu, dünyamı korur. Tüm bunlar bir yana, senin gibi dışlanmış Keşiftör kastına mensup paslı bir hurdanın bana 'cahil' demesine müsaade etmem!"

traits.locale_text: "Haneumann mı? Yalancı, o sen değilsin. Dementz Haneumann bana itaat ediyor, zihni uçsuzun seslerine açık ve yarattığı hurda kodu dünyamı koruyor. Ayrıca senin gibi dışlanmış Keşiftör kastına mensup paslı hurdaların bana 'cahil' demesine izin vermeyeceğim!"
